channel.title: 503 Error on most sites when using Kali Linux + Whonix
channel.description: For Example, when trying to reach Reddit, I get a 503 error. As well as other sites as well. Some sites don't get the error, some do, and it's quite annoying. I don't know what I'm doing wrong or how to fix it, as I'm a noob.
